OSPFv3 Multi-Area Cisco IOS

Router01
configure terminal
opv6 router ospf 1
router-id 10.0.0.1
passive-interface loopback 0
interface gi0/1
ipv6 ospf cost 10
ipv6 ospf 1 area 0.0.0.0
interface gi0/2
ipv6 ospf cost 10
ipv6 ospf 1 area 0.0.0.0
interface loopback 0 
ipv6 ospf cost 10
ipv6 ospf 1 area 0.0.0.0

show ipv6 ospf interface brief
show ipv6 ospf neighbor
show ipv6 ospf database


